<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gorge1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gorge,</orth> subst. the throat, the swallow, the stomach: <cit><quote>till g. be stuffed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 58" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 58</bibl></cit>. <emph>he cracks his</emph> <cit><quote>g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 44</bibl></cit> (i. e. by endeavouring to vomit). <cit><quote>cast the g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 40</bibl></cit> (== vomit). <cit><quote>my g. rises at it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.207" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 207</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to heave the g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.236" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 236</bibl></cit> (== to retch).
<pb n="487" />
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>